<DOCNO>GH950203-000007</DOCNO>
<DOCID>GH950203-000007</DOCID>
<DATE>950203</DATE>
<HEADLINE>Cricket</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>46</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>980041877</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
IAN Beven, the 36-year-old veteran off-spinner, has left Grange and
joined West Lothian.
Beven, who won every honour in his time at Raeburn Place, said: ''I've
had nine fantastic seasons at Grange, but everything comes to an end and
the time has come to move on.''
</TEXT>
